txt.en: 'Hullo! Hullo! If it isn't the great warrior! Slay any great worms of late, mighty knight?'
'You mind your tongue, or I'll give you the back of my shield!'
'Why not? We'll see how well your shield stands against my hammer!'
'I've seen stones thicker than that board strapped to your arm shatter under Cooper's hammer.'
'Adso should have left the two of you in the pig sty he found you in! It will be two seasons before that inn even has a roof on it.'
'I can knock things down faster than I can build them up. Shall I show you?'
'All right then, how about that one?'
